<div class="nibbles">
    <%= render HeadingComponent.new(title: "Nibbles", tone: :blue, size: :full) %>
    <div class="nibbles__sidequests">
        <h1 class="nibbles__sidequests-subtitle">Tackle fun sidequests for extra (bite-sized) challenges and tasty bonuses!</h1>
        <div class="nibbles__sidequests-cards">
            <%= render SidequestCardComponent.new(
                title: "The Hackazine",
                image: "nibbles/Hackazine.avif",
                sticker_image: "nibbles/Hackazine-Sticker.avif",
                description: "This January: make a page for your project and get it in the Hack Club 2025 magazine! Join #magazine and submit before January 22nd. Projects selected for the magazine receive 50 cookies + stickers! Please note, magazine submissions have 0% AI tolerance.",
                learn_more_link: "https://magazine.hackclub.com/",
                submit_link: "https://hackclub.slack.com/app_redirect?channel=C0A8CMWM0CR",
                variant: :red
            ) %>
            <%= render SidequestCardComponent.new(
                title: "Borked UI Jam",
                image: "nibbles/Borked-UI-Jam.avif",
                description: "Running until January 25th â€” make a project with delightfully broken UI/UX and submit it for the Borked UI Jam! The top 5 best (worst) projects will receive cookies + other prizes. Check out #borked for more details.",
                learn_more_link: "https://hackclub.slack.com/app_redirect?channel=C0A278BH8UA",
                submit_link: "https://borked.irtaza.xyz/",
                variant: :green
            ) %>
            <div id="challenger-center" class="sidequest-card sidequest-card--purple" data-controller="sidequest-expand">
                <div class="sidequest-card__content">
                    <h1 class="sidequest-card__title">Meet an Astronaut</h1>
                    <div class="sidequest-card__image-container">
                        <%= image_tag "launch/rocket.png", alt: "Space Mission", class: "sidequest-card__image" %>
                    </div>
                    <h2>NASA has a list of tech problems they can't solve. Think you can help? Build something space-worthy and you might get flown out to hang with a real astronaut.</h2>
                </div>

                <div class="sidequest-card__expanded" data-sidequest-expand-target="content">
                    <div class="sidequest-card__expanded-inner">
                        <h2 class="sidequest-card__expanded-title">Space Smells Like Raspberries and Cookies</h2>
                        <p class="sidequest-card__expanded-text">
                            Seriously, astronauts say it smells like rum and raspberries out there. Build something that helps humans survive in space and you could find out for yourself.
                        </p>

                        <div class="sidequest-card__expanded-grid">
                            <div class="sidequest-card__expanded-cell">
                                <p>Check out <%= link_to "NASA's list of unsolved tech problems", "https://techport.nasa.gov/strategy", target: "_blank", rel: "noopener noreferrer", class: "sidequest-card__link" %> and build something that tackles one</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="sidequest-card__expanded-cell">
                                <p>Solar storms, radiation shielding, growing food on Mars - pick a problem that sounds cool and hack on it</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="sidequest-card__expanded-cell">
                                <p>Websites, apps, games, hardware, whatever. If you could use it on the moon, we want to see it</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="sidequest-card__buttons">
                    <button class="btn btn--blue btn-learn-more" data-action="sidequest-expand#toggle" data-sidequest-expand-target="button">
                        <span data-sidequest-expand-target="buttonText">Learn More</span>
                    </button>
                    <%= link_to "Submit", kitchen_path, class: "btn btn--green btn-submit" %>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
